data.name: ASML Holding NV
data.description: ASML Holding NV (ASML) is the Netherlands-based holding company active in the field of technology. The Company is a provider of advanced semiconductor equipment systems, consisting of lithographic systems. It offers an integrated portfolio of products mainly for manufacturing complex integrated circuits (IC), semiconductors or chips. The Company reports one segment, System sales, divided in New Systems and Used Systems. It supplies lithography systems to IC manufacturers throughout Asia, the United States and Europe. Additionally, the Company is engaged in service and field option sales. It provides its customers with a range of support services from advanced process and product applications knowledge to round-the-clock service support. ASML's main wholly owned operating subsidiaries include ASML Netherlands BV, ASML Systems BV, ASML Hong Kong Limited and ASML US Inc. In May 2013, Cymer Inc completed the previously announced merger pursuant to which ASML Holding NV acquired Cymer.
